空氣污染工程學-袁中新老師














課程進度



1
2011/09/12~2011/09/18
Course Description


2
2011/09/19~2011/09/25
Effects and Sources of Air Pollutants


3
2011/09/26~2011/10/02
Air Pollution Terminology and Visibility Degradation


4
2011/10/03~2011/10/09
Legislation and Regulations Related to Air Pollution


5
2011/10/10~2011/10/16
Meteorology and Characteristics of Stack Plume


6
2011/10/17~2011/10/23
Dispersion of Air Pollutants


7
2011/10/24~2011/10/30
Characteristics of Particulate Matter


8
2011/10/31~2011/11/06
General Control of Particulate Matter (I)


9
2011/11/07~2011/11/13
General Control of Particulate Matter (II)


10
2011/11/14~2011/11/20
Characteristics of Gases and Vapors


11
2011/11/21~2011/11/27
General Control of Gases and Vapors (I)


12
2011/11/28~2011/12/04
General Control of Gases and Vapors (II)


13
2011/12/05~2011/12/11
Control of Sulfur Dioxide


14
2011/12/12~2011/12/18
Control of Nitrogen Oxides


15
2011/12/19~2011/12/25
Field Trip


16
2011/12/26~2012/01/01
Mobile Source Control


17
2012/01/02~2012/01/06
Odor Control


18
2012/01/07~2012/01/13
Final Report and Oral Presentation



